        <p class="text-sm text-graphite">Testing 48 LLMs across 5 dimensions for $4.63.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/reports/mcp-tool-test" class="group block border border-ink/10 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-petrol/30 transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-ink group-hover:text-petrol transition-colors mb-1">MCP Tool Test</h3>
